	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf02dd1929.jpg" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">为什么呢？</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">　　优秀的项目，需要照明设计、灯具设备、灯光调试的通力协作，缺一不可，可是这三个方面，我们都有所欠缺。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">　　照明设计师作为建筑或室内设计师的灯光顾问，起着非常重要的作用。在室外亮化，酒店，专卖店空间等都有非常专业的照明设计师，但是，在博物馆照明领域，人才却非常缺乏：</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:center;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span class="" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="11" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">1</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">　　博物馆照明作为一个细分市场，容量不大．虽然近年来国家在博物馆事业方面投入很大，但与其它行业相比，它还是体量小，专业从事设计的人才比较少。</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span class="" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="12" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">2</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">　　博物馆照明项目相对于室外亮化、酒店、专卖店等，工程体量小，相应的设计费也低。譬如室外亮化工程，灯光轻松上亿，照明设计费动辄数百万以至千万。而一个博物馆照明工程总共几百万，很少上千万！相应的设计费几十万而已，因此吸引力大不如前者。</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf04e15b3c.jpg" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span class="" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="13" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">3</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">　　博物馆照明工程空间复杂，工作量大。相对于酒店照明工程，大部分区域是客房，而客房照明绝大多数是统一的，这让工作量一下子少了很多，专卖店也是如此。可是博物馆每个空间的照明都不一样，展品也不一样，没有可复制的，工作量大了很多。</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">　　所以，现实而言，专注于博物馆照明的人才或企业，相对于其它照明领域，收益与付出是不成比例的。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">　　因此，我们很难看到专注博物馆照明的设计师或设计公司。虽然专注于室外亮化、酒店、商业连锁空间的比比皆是。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf06d72785.jpg" width="340" height="362" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">目前我们只发现一些兼做博物馆照明的设计师或者设计公司。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">原因也很简单，如果专注博物馆的话，他们很难生存。在这种情况下，专业人才就难培育出来。那么，遇到博物馆照明项目怎么办呢？</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf0e49d6b8.jpg" width="300" height="236" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">找一些做过博物馆照明设计的公司或者设计师来做，由于多方面因素影响，能出杰作的比较少。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">但是，市场发展起来了，需求上来了，怎么办呢？</span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">一些专注做博物馆产品的企业，会配置一些照明设计师，用于项目的配灯或者照明设计。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">这种情况会有先天不足，如产品单一性，设计师的视野不足等，输出也多以布灯配灯为主。只能勉强为之。当然，也有的产品配套企业成立专业团队，这样会好一些。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">　　因设计而造成的先天不足，是否会在后天得到弥补呢？</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<em style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">2</span></strong></em> 
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="92724" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px auto;padding:10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:2px 0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;display:inline-block;border-bottom-width:1px;border-bottom-style:dotted;border-color:#D9AB2B;"><section class="" data-brushtype="text" style="text-align:left;margin:0px;padding:5px 8px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#FFFFFF;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;"><span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">市场呼唤调灯师</span></section></section></section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">　　事实上，博物馆除了先天不足，还存在后天不良。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">　　博物馆照明有一种说法＂三分灯光七分调＂，它过于强调了灯光调试的作用，但是也从侧面说明了灯光调试的重要性。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">　　博物馆陈列空间，展品大小不一，而且在设计阶段，对于展品很少有详细的规划，灯光只能粗略的布置，那么，要实现精准调光，就只能靠调灯师的细致工作了。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">　　而且博物馆临展很多，每次灯光都要改动，临展常常缺乏专业的照明设计与技术指导，这时只能靠调灯师了！</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf15114bfa.jpg" width="320" height="196" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">可是博物馆照明调灯师，目前这种职业都没有！没有职业，谈何人才？</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">目前这个工作被电工、维修工、厂家或施工方技术人员、照明设计师等兼做了．每种人才缺乏专业训练，个人经验过于依赖，这样，调出来的效果也是参差不齐。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">而且由于调灯师没有职业资格认证，大家普遍不太认同他们工作的专业性，所以在灯光调试的时候，室内设计师、专家、领导都会关注，对于灯光的意见尤其多，由于调灯师没有相应的地位，大家也不太认同，都希望灯光调出自己想要的样子，结果是调灯师忙前忙后，最后的效果却差强人意！</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf16b3bc8b.jpg" width="300" height="200" alt="" />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;font-weight:bold;text-align:left;">先天不足与后天不良已经让博物馆照明不堪重负，还有观念问题更是让博物馆照明雪上加霜！</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span class="" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="9" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">1</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">　　任何一个博物馆，无论做得多精彩，如果灯光不行，都无法展现好的效果。但其实大家愿意在其它方面花大笔资金，舍不得在照明上多花钱。某些项目资金不足，实施过程中，各个分项都会挪用。照明在最后，结果做的时候发现资金已经挪用完了！没办法，只能凑合着做掉。</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf189550e6.jpg" width="320" height="214" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span class="" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="10" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">2</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">　　如今很多博物馆逐渐重视灯光了，财政部办公厅于2017年1月5日颁布的财办预 (2017)56号文件印发《陈列展览项目支出预算方案编制规范和预算编制标准试行办法》，对于相关预算规定如下表：</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf1a2e8ac6.jpg" width="314" height="457" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">对于灯光，多媒体分别规定了相关费用，这根本上强调了灯光的重要性。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:1px;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">　　<b>还有一个普遍的误区，</b></span></span><span style="letter-spacing:1px;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">大家认为博物馆照明的投入，就是灯具设备的费用，没有考虑照明设计，灯光调试……结果我们看到太多失败的例子：投入巨资，上了一堆大牌设备，最后呈现的效果很差！</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf1b9c5467.jpg" width="320" height="183" alt="" />
</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="text-align:left;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">　　博物馆灯光越来越被重视，投入越大</span><strong style="text-align:left;color:#595959;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">，过于强调设备却忽略设计与调试，造成资源浪费而难以出效果。</span></strong><span style="text-align:left;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">这种现象会越来越严重，需要注意！</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><em style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">3</span></em></strong> 
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="92724" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px auto;padding:10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:2px 0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;display:inline-block;border-bottom-width:1px;border-bottom-style:dotted;border-color:#D9AB2B;"><section class="" data-brushtype="text" style="text-align:left;margin:0px;padding:5px 8px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#FFFFFF;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;"><span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">博物馆照明的＂诗与远方＂</span></section></section></section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">照明设计师，调灯师——</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<em style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">一方是渴求的市场，</span></strong></em> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<em style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">一方是奇缺的人才</span></strong></em><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">。</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">&nbsp; 　　博物馆照明如何突破呢？</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">&nbsp; 　　笔者根据多年的从业经验，提出一些建议供参考：</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf1ce571ea.jpg" width="400" height="231" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="134" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:1em 0px 0.5em;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;clear:both;border:0px none;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:1em;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section class="" data-brushtype="text" style="margin:0px;padding:0px 0.5em;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;display:inline-block;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#D9AB2B;"><span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">1.&nbsp; 馆方或施工企业，配置专业的调灯师。</span></section></section></section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">无论是常设展还是临展，调灯是馆方常有的工作，因此，配置专业的调灯师是亟待解决的问题。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">　　目前这些工作多由馆内电工来完成，有些电工依据自己多年的经验，综合专家或者设计师的建议，也能调出不错的效果，但是，如果项目比较复杂，设计师、专家、领导等意见多，电工就很难调试了。　　</span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">可行的办法是让电工做一些专业培训，掌握照明知识，辅以实际项目经验，成为一位合格的调灯师，这些问题就能迎刃而解。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf1e4ef08e.jpg" width="400" height="255" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">&nbsp; 　　具体来说，那些知识包括：</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span class="" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="6" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">1</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">　　室内设计图与布灯图的阅读，灵活运用，布灯必须熟知相关图纸，并能根据场景的变化灵活运用。</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span class="" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="7" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">2</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">　　光学配件应用．如果调灯师掌握了光学配件的应用，就能灵活自如根据展示物而改变光斑大小于形状。</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">3</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">　　灯具产品知识，熟知各类厂家的产品参数与特性，在不同的场景中选用合适的灯具。</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:1.5;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;"><span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:1.5;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">照明艺术，懂一点艺术是很有必要的，至少能够理解设计师的意图，通过灯光来表达。</span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">而这些培训应该是不定期的，如此能把握最新技术，共享互通。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf2001e336.jpg" width="376" height="250" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="134" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;">
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:1em;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;color:#FEFEFE;line-height:2em;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-brushtype="text" style="margin:0px;padding:0px 0.5em;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;display:inline-block;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#D9AB2B;">
<div style="text-align:left;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:0.544px;">2.&nbsp;博物馆展陈设计公司或施工公司设立照明设计组，聘用专业的照明设计师作为照明顾问。</span>
</div>
</section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
</section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#595959;"><span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">　　展陈设计公司负责博物馆室内整体设计，对于灯光，最好有专业的设计师团队来实现整体效果，</span><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">任何博物馆项目，整体表现的最后一道关口就是灯光，这个节点需要足够重视并把握好。</span></strong></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">国内有照明设计师这个职业，展陈企业通过配置专业的照明设计师，使其专注于博物馆照明领域，对于项目设计及后期效果呈现，会得到有力的保障！</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">目前这部分工作外包比较多，即便外包也要自己懂，如果自己一点不懂，直接交给外面，效果很难保障。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">　　另外，照明设计是在室内设计的基础上进行了，照明设计师需要充分理解室内设计师及建筑师的意图，这些工作比较细致，而外包的话，这些很细致的工作很难做到位，如果自己没有照明设计方面的人才，很难做出想要的效果。</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf2182ebe4.jpg" width="376" height="252" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="134" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:1em 0px 0.5em;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;clear:both;border:0px none;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:1em;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section class="" data-brushtype="text" style="margin:0px;padding:0px 0.5em;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;word-wrap:break-word !important;display:inline-block;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#D9AB2B;"><span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">3.&nbsp;对于照明设备与效果评测的第三方企业</span></section></section></section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;"><br />
</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;"><span style="caret-color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.5440000295639038px;">　　</span></span><span style="color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;letter-spacing:1px;">对于照明设备，目前我们还是土豪式的做法，选最好的抑或最贵的．其实不同情况要区别对待：</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span class="" data-original-title="" title="" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">1</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;">　　博物馆环境照明并不需要非常专业的灯光，适当即可。</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span class="" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="2" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">2</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;">　　各类厂家产品优势不一样，有的强于重点照明，有点长于洗墙照明，我们要综合考虑，选其优点。而目前来看，还没有一家企业的灯具在所有的博物馆照明空间做得最好。</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span class="" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="3" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">3</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;">　　博物馆领域口口相传或者示范效应比较强，这样容易忽略一些优秀的，名气小但有特点的产品，但他们都能达到要求，可能性能更好，价格更实惠。</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf22f0ae4c.jpg" width="234" height="324" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span class="" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="4" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">4</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">　　那在这种情况下，具备权威性的第三方机构，如果能提供专业建议与独立报告，给业主或者馆方决策提供意见。这样能节省成本并确保效果。目前关于灯具方面，只有一个有关安全的CCC认证，而关于效果灯具性能等方面，权威的评测机构几乎没有。</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89413" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;border:0px none;background-color:#FFFFFF;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><section style="text-align:left;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:40px;height:40px;border:2px solid #D9AB2B;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;background-color:#FEFEFE;word-wrap:break-word !important;"></section><section style="text-align:center;margin:-34px 0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:30px;height:30px;border-top-left-radius:50%;border-top-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-right-radius:50%;border-bottom-left-radius:50%;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:30px;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;transform:rotate(0deg);background-color:#D9AB2B;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span class="" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="5" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">5</span></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:23px 10px 10px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;min-height:1em;border-top-width:2px;border-top-style:solid;border-color:#D9AB2B;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;background-color:#F5F5F5;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;">　　当然，一些机构开始尝试，如北京清控人居光电研究院，在艾晶主持的2017 年度文化行业标准化研究项目“美术馆照明质量评估＂中，开始对一些博物馆专业照明企业的产品进行独立评估，对于馆方全面了解市场行情，产品功能特性，是非常有益的。</span> 
</p>
</section></section>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/04/09/u5cabf24650ce7.jpg" width="376" height="207" alt="" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;white-space:normal;widows:1;line-height:2em;letter-spacing:1px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;color:#595959;font-family:SimSun;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.5;">　　当照明设计、灯具设备、灯光调试问题都得到有效解决了，现状才会从根本上改善，真正迎来博物馆照明的＂诗与远方＂。</span> 
</p>						</div>
											</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
